snippet.title: Walking Dead Definitive Series - Graphic Black Teaser (EU)
snippet.description:
PEGI Rating: 18

With The Walking Dead: Telltale Definitive Series, step into the world of #Clementine and #Lee with all new Graphic Black visual enhancements, invoking the feel of Robert Kirkman's seminal comic itself!

The StillNotBitten team has worked tirelessly to update every inch of the game to match the quality of The Final Season - this is just a small taste of the visual changes, sync improvements, and more! 

Preorder RIGHT NOW to get the Standard Pack complete with all the amazing digital bonus content, like in-game soundtrack player, concept art gallery, and so much more!

For full details and to order now, click here: http://bit.ly/TWD_DefSeries
